metainfo.about:
Framework phpMeccano gives API:
to create and manage groups of users;
to authenticate users;
to control access to functions by using group policies;
to create multilingual interface;
to copy, move and remove local files and folders;
to log events;
to create and share messages and files between contacts of users like in simple social network;
to create topics to discuss and comment them.
System of plugins allows to extend functionality and to add new features.
Current version is still the alpha version.
